[The above report is an apt summation of the challenges in keeping track of the emerging SARS-CoV-2 variants and the potential impact on vaccination and therapeutics. More importantly, this has implications for when the countries can scale down on the social distancing restrictions and the concurrent public safety and transmission issues. - Mod.UBA]

